<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>导航窗格示例</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .navbar a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: #f2f2f2;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        .navbar a.active {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="navbar">
    <a href="#home" class="active">首页</a>
    <a href="#services">服务</a>
    <a href="#about">关于我们</a>
    <a href="#contact">联系我们</a>
</div>

<div style="padding:16px">
    <h1>欢迎访问我们的网站</h1>
    <p>这里是内容区域，可以放置您网站的主要内容。</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
